    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? You\u2019ve gotta see this car! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, and it's been kept in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! Come check it out, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
